locations: Hollywood Blvd., Hollywood, California, USA::(street scenes)
imdb.plot outline: On Hollywood Blvd, in Hollywood, California, they ask pedestrians - locals and tourists, WHAT DO YOU KNOW ABOUT GREECE? How much do you actually know about Greece? You'll be surprised at some of the Answers. There are tongue twisters, crazy Greek words, Movies, and products. It's a new meaning to the saying, 'It's All Greek to Me'. From the Director of "We Love Cyprus", Constantinos Isaias brings this New Web Reality Series, "What do you know about Greece" to Your Screen. The first 9 Episodes are Ready! Test your Greek knowledge. Each episode is captivating and hilarious, and might even teach you a little something. So, Lights, Camera, OPA!
